<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. A lul nau e thilhing chitin,
 Lungguol in tang hih hawih ui;
 Van Mang paknan zaila a awi ui,
 &quot;Aw Lal lopipen&quot; ti'n la a sau.

[V2]
 Aw Hallelujah, chungnungpen,
 Lei mun thawmhau leh Na sulnung gamthip ahin;
 Nang hun ngaia chauin a mau ui,
 Suihlung muonna Lalpa hung lengin.

[V3]
 2. Sietlei hin khuo zanbang thimah;
 Lalpa min thei bang lo ka;
 Hin kiemlo gam tun kal ka ngak lah,;
 Hung vakin, kumsawt tawplo gam chu.

[V4]
 3. Damlai ni kawlah tum mahleh,
 Ka ngak Kanaan khawpi chu;
 Hung vak ina nitum senglo gam,
 Nawpna kim tana Lallukhuk tawh.

[V5]
 4. Lal lenna Zion gal muongah,
 Aw lei leh van Lalpa chu;
 &quot;Hallelujah tia zaila sa'n,
 Angel tawh Lalchutphah kimvel in.</lyrics>
<title>Hallelujah Chungnungpen !</title>
<hymn_number>91</hymn_number>
</song>